verse: Alleluia, Alleluia, Alleluia, Praise the Lord.
He is risen, Alleluia; He is risen, Alleluia,
He is risen, Alleluia; He is risen,
He is risen, Alleluia; He is risen, Alleluia,
He is risen, Alleluia; He is risen,
Jesus loves me, this I know; for the Bible
tells me so. Little ones to Him belong
They are weak, but he is strong.
What a friend we have in Jesus,
All our sins and griefs to bear;
Every thing to God in prayer.
Alleluia, Alleluia, Alleluia, Praise the Lord.
